            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>conchiglie</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>conchiglie</strong> for 6-8 min</p><p>Tip: It doesn't need to be fully cooked, as it will go in the oven later!</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> conchiglie</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1603112150626-x200.jpg",
