            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is softening, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>with the <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1603112167465-x200.jpg",
