            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>roasted pepper & mushrooms</strong> to the pan with the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong>,<strong> Henderson's Relish </strong>and <strong>soured cream</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Season with a crack of <strong>black pepper </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>smoky sauce</strong></p><p>Grate the<strong> cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1603112182778-x200.jpg",
